# Spell Trivia — stable v1

`spell` is tagged `stable: 'v1'` in `src/platform/catalog.ts`. See `STABLE.md`.

## Do not change

Unless the user **explicitly** asks to modify Spell Trivia:

- Do not edit files under `src/games/spell/` or `games/spell/`
- Do not change spelling bank wiring, scoring, or quiz UX in game-specific files

## Instead

- Fix quiz UX via shared modules (`freeQuizShell.ts`, `_quiz/style.css`, `freeShellNav.ts`, `_quiz/adapters.ts` only when all quiz games need it)
- If a shared change affects Spell Trivia, **tell the user** which shared file changed and why
